---
// Silica Technology Page - Professional design
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Technology - Silica Protocol" description="Deep dive into Silica's advanced consensus mechanism, performance benchmarks, and post-quantum security features">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-950 via-slate-900 to-slate-950 text-white py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Animated Background Nodes -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(14,165,233,0.3) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(14,165,233,0.3) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-cyan-500/20 blur-[120px] animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 4s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-1/3 right-1/4 w-[350px] h-[350px] rounded-full bg-teal-500/15 blur-[100px] animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 6s;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
          Revolutionary <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-teal-400 to-green-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Technology</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-cyan-100/90 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Discover the cutting-edge consensus mechanism, unparalleled performance, and future-proof security that powers Silica Protocol.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Consensus Architecture Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Consensus Architecture
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          A layered pipeline: Alluvium (data availability) → Crystallite (ordering) → The Striation (parallel execution) → Calib (verification + watchdog / Arb) → Lithification (irreversible finality), with periodic anchors (Lineation/Lineament).
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Architecture Note / Disclaimer -->
      <div class="bg-cyan-500/10 border-l-4 border-cyan-500 rounded-r-lg p-6 mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Architecture Note</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
              This page reflects the current architecture source of truth. Implementation details and performance metrics evolve as we optimize the network. For technical implementation details, see the 
              <a href="https://github.com/Silica-Protocol/Silica-Protocol" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">GitHub repository</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Animated Consensus Flow Diagram -->
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-cyan-500/20 p-8 mb-12">
        <!-- Timeline Style Consensus Architecture -->
        <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Central Timeline Line -->
          <div class="hidden lg:block absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-cyan-500 via-teal-500 to-green-500 h-full opacity-30"></div>

          <!-- Phase 1: Alluvium (Left Side) -->
          <div class="relative mb-16">
            <div class="lg:flex items-center">
              <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-12 mb-6 lg:mb-0">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/20 to-cyan-600/10 border border-cyan-500/30 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-cyan-500/30 transition-all duration-300">
                  <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg p-3 mr-4">
                      <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10\"></path>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-cyan-400 mb-1">LAYER 1 • DATA PLANE</div>
                      <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Alluvium</h3>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-slate-200 mb-4">Parallel transaction batching and high-throughput data availability layer using DAG structure.</p>
                  <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">•</span>
                      Workers gossip transaction batches in parallel across network
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">•</span>
                      DAG-based causal structure with batch references
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">•</span>
                      Separates data dissemination from consensus ordering
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">•</span>
                      Enables horizontal scaling without security compromise
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <!-- Animated Batches -->\n                  <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2">
                    <div class="w-12 h-2 bg-cyan-400 rounded animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 1s;"></div>
                    <div class="w-12 h-2 bg-cyan-400 rounded animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 1.2s;"></div>
                    <div class="w-12 h-2 bg-cyan-400 rounded animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 1.4s;"></div>
                    <div class="w-12 h-2 bg-cyan-400 rounded animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 1.6s;"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden lg:block absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-900 shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/50"></div>
              <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-12">
                <div class="consensus-anim consensus-anim--alluvium" aria-hidden="true">
                  <div class="consensus-anim__label">Alluvium: batching + gossip</div>
                  <svg class="consensus-anim__svg" viewBox="0 0 320 180" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" focusable="false">
                    <defs>
                      <linearGradient id="alluviumFlow" x1="0" y1="0" x2="320" y2="0" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                        <stop stop-color="#22D3EE" stop-opacity="0.9" />
                        <stop offset="1" stop-color="#14B8A6" stop-opacity="0.9" />
                      </linearGradient>
                    </defs>

                    <rect x="36" y="48" width="128" height="84" rx="14" stroke="#22D3EE" stroke-opacity="0.55" stroke-width="2" />
                    <rect x="44" y="56" width="112" height="30" rx="10" fill="#22D3EE" fill-opacity="0.12" />
                    <rect class="alluvium-batch" x="44" y="92" width="112" height="30" rx="10" fill="url(#alluviumFlow)" fill-opacity="0.72" />

                    <g class="alluvium-tx alluvium-tx--a">
                      <rect x="66" y="18" width="18" height="18" rx="5" fill="#22D3EE" fill-opacity="0.9" />
                    </g>
                    <g class="alluvium-tx alluvium-tx--b">
                      <rect x="102" y="10" width="18" height="18" rx="5" fill="#22D3EE" fill-opacity="0.75" />
                    </g>
                    <g class="alluvium-tx alluvium-tx--c">
                      <rect x="138" y="20" width="18" height="18" rx="5" fill="#22D3EE" fill-opacity="0.65" />
                    </g>

                    <path d="M188 107h86" stroke="url(#alluviumFlow)" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-opacity="0.6" />
                    <path class="alluvium-arrow" d="M260 94l20 13-20 13" fill="url(#alluviumFlow)" fill-opacity="0.75" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Phase 2: Crystallite (Right Side) -->
          <div class="relative mb-16">
            <div class="lg:flex items-center">
              <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-12">
                <div class="consensus-anim consensus-anim--crystallite" aria-hidden="true">
                  <div class="consensus-anim__label">Crystallite: deterministic ordering</div>
                  <svg class="consensus-anim__svg" viewBox="0 0 320 180" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" focusable="false">
                    <defs>
                      <linearGradient id="crystalOrder" x1="0" y1="0" x2="320" y2="0" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                        <stop stop-color="#22D3EE" stop-opacity="0.9" />
                        <stop offset="1" stop-color="#2DD4BF" stop-opacity="0.9" />
                      </linearGradient>
                    </defs>

                    <rect x="34" y="48" width="252" height="84" rx="18" stroke="#2DD4BF" stroke-opacity="0.35" stroke-width="2" />
                    <path d="M62 90h196" stroke="url(#crystalOrder)" stroke-opacity="0.5" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />

                    <g class="crystal-block crystal-block--one">
                      <rect x="62" y="64" width="52" height="52" rx="14" fill="#2DD4BF" fill-opacity="0.16" stroke="#2DD4BF" stroke-opacity="0.55" />
                      <text x="88" y="98" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18" font-weight="700" fill="#5EEAD4">?</text>
                    </g>
                    <g class="crystal-block crystal-block--two">
                      <rect x="134" y="64" width="52" height="52" rx="14" fill="#2DD4BF" fill-opacity="0.16" stroke="#2DD4BF" stroke-opacity="0.55" />
                      <text x="160" y="98" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18" font-weight="700" fill="#5EEAD4">?</text>
                    </g>
                    <g class="crystal-block crystal-block--three">
                      <rect x="206" y="64" width="52" height="52" rx="14" fill="#2DD4BF" fill-opacity="0.16" stroke="#2DD4BF" stroke-opacity="0.55" />
                      <text x="232" y="98" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18" font-weight="700" fill="#5EEAD4">?</text>
                    </g>

                    <g class="crystal-orderline" opacity="0">
                      <rect x="62" y="64" width="52" height="52" rx="14" fill="url(#crystalOrder)" fill-opacity="0.62" />
                      <text x="88" y="98" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18" font-weight="800" fill="#0F172A">1</text>
                      <rect x="134" y="64" width="52" height="52" rx="14" fill="url(#crystalOrder)" fill-opacity="0.62" />
                      <text x="160" y="98" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18" font-weight="800" fill="#0F172A">2</text>
                      <rect x="206" y="64" width="52" height="52" rx="14" fill="url(#crystalOrder)" fill-opacity="0.62" />
                      <text x="232" y="98" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18" font-weight="800" fill="#0F172A">3</text>
                    </g>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden lg:block absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-teal-600 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-900 shadow-lg shadow-teal-500/50"></div>
              <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-12">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500/20 to-teal-600/10 border border-teal-500/30 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-teal-500/30 transition-all duration-300">
                  <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-teal-600 rounded-lg p-3 mr-4">
                      <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-teal-400 mb-1">LAYER 2 • ORDERING</div>
                      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Crystallite</h3>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-slate-200 mb-4">Deterministic DAG commit rules and linearization producing canonical transaction ordering.</p>
                  <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="text-teal-400 mr-2">•</span>
                      Structural DAG commit rules ensure deterministic ordering
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="text-teal-400 mr-2">•</span>
                      Linearizer outputs identical CommittedSubDag sequences
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="text-teal-400 mr-2">•</span>
                      No timing-dependent or arrival-order behaviors
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="text-teal-400 mr-2">•</span>
                      Source of truth: CommittedSubDag from linearizer
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <!-- Animated Ordering -->
                  <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <div class="flex-1 h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-teal-400 rounded animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 2s;"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

           <!-- Phase 3: The Striation (Left Side) -->
           <div class="relative mb-16">
             <div class="lg:flex items-center">
               <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-12 mb-6 lg:mb-0">
                 <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/20 to-indigo-600/10 border border-indigo-500/30 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-indigo-500/30 transition-all duration-300">
                   <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                     <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-lg p-3 mr-4">
                       <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                         <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"></path>
                       </svg>
                     </div>
                     <div>
                       <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-1">LAYER 3 • EXECUTION</div>
                       <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">The Striation</h3>
                     </div>
                   </div>
                   <p class="text-slate-200 mb-4">Parallel execution framework that routes ordered transactions into deterministic execution lanes (Striae).</p>
                   <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                     <li class="flex items-start">
                       <span class="text-indigo-400 mr-2">•</span>
                       Schedules ordered transactions for parallelism
                     </li>
                     <li class="flex items-start">
                       <span class="text-indigo-400 mr-2">•</span>
                       Each Stria is a single deterministic execution context
                     </li>
                     <li class="flex items-start">
                       <span class="text-indigo-400 mr-2">•</span>
                       Determinism preserved across replicas
                     </li>
                     <li class="flex items-start">
                       <span class="text-indigo-400 mr-2">•</span>
                       Maximizes throughput without re-ordering
                     </li>
                   </ul>
                   <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                     <div class="w-10 h-2 bg-indigo-400 rounded animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 1.2s;"></div>
                     <div class="w-10 h-2 bg-indigo-400 rounded animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 1.4s;"></div>
                     <div class="w-10 h-2 bg-indigo-400 rounded animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 1.6s;"></div>
                   </div>
                 </div>
               </div>
               <div class="hidden lg:block absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-900 shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/50"></div>
               <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-12">
                  <div class="consensus-anim consensus-anim--striation" aria-hidden="true">
                   <div class="consensus-anim__label">Striation: route txs → accounts</div>
                   <svg class="consensus-anim__svg" viewBox="0 0 320 180" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" focusable="false">
                     <defs>
                       <linearGradient id="striaFlow" x1="0" y1="0" x2="320" y2="0" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                         <stop stop-color="#818CF8" stop-opacity="0.95" />
                         <stop offset="1" stop-color="#60A5FA" stop-opacity="0.95" />
                       </linearGradient>
                     </defs>

                     <rect x="36" y="44" width="248" height="92" rx="18" stroke="#818CF8" stroke-opacity="0.32" stroke-width="2" />

                     <!-- Small DAG cluster (incoming ordered txs) -->
                     <g opacity="0.8">
                       <circle cx="62" cy="66" r="6" fill="#818CF8" fill-opacity="0.55" />
                       <circle cx="52" cy="92" r="6" fill="#818CF8" fill-opacity="0.4" />
                       <circle cx="74" cy="104" r="6" fill="#818CF8" fill-opacity="0.45" />
                       <circle cx="64" cy="122" r="6" fill="#818CF8" fill-opacity="0.35" />
                       <path d="M62 66L52 92L74 104L64 122" stroke="#818CF8" stroke-opacity="0.35" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
                     </g>

                     <!-- Execution lanes -->
                     <path d="M92 69C132 69 152 60 190 60" stroke="url(#striaFlow)" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-opacity="0.52" />
                     <path d="M92 101C132 101 152 101 190 101" stroke="url(#striaFlow)" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-opacity="0.42" />
                     <path d="M92 133C132 133 152 142 190 142" stroke="url(#striaFlow)" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-opacity="0.32" />

                     <!-- Account state blocks -->
                     <g class="stria-account stria-account--a">
                       <rect class="stria-account-shell" x="198" y="48" width="78" height="30" rx="12" fill="#0F172A" fill-opacity="0.35" stroke="#818CF8" stroke-opacity="0.35" />
                       <rect class="stria-account-fill stria-account-fill--a" x="206" y="66" width="62" height="6" rx="3" fill="url(#striaFlow)" fill-opacity="0.7" />
                       <text x="237" y="67" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" font-weight="700" fill="#E2E8F0" fill-opacity="0.75">acct</text>
                     </g>
                     <g class="stria-account stria-account--b">
                       <rect class="stria-account-shell" x="198" y="80" width="78" height="30" rx="12" fill="#0F172A" fill-opacity="0.35" stroke="#818CF8" stroke-opacity="0.35" />
                       <rect class="stria-account-fill stria-account-fill--b" x="206" y="98" width="62" height="6" rx="3" fill="url(#striaFlow)" fill-opacity="0.55" />
                       <text x="237" y="99" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" font-weight="700" fill="#E2E8F0" fill-opacity="0.75">acct</text>
                     </g>
                     <g class="stria-account stria-account--c">
                       <rect class="stria-account-shell" x="198" y="112" width="78" height="30" rx="12" fill="#0F172A" fill-opacity="0.35" stroke="#818CF8" stroke-opacity="0.35" />
                       <rect class="stria-account-fill stria-account-fill--c" x="206" y="130" width="62" height="6" rx="3" fill="url(#striaFlow)" fill-opacity="0.4" />
                       <text x="237" y="131" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" font-weight="700" fill="#E2E8F0" fill-opacity="0.75">acct</text>
                     </g>

                     <!-- Transactions routed into lanes -->
                     <circle class="stria-tx stria-tx--a" cx="92" cy="69" r="7" fill="url(#striaFlow)" />
                     <circle class="stria-tx stria-tx--b" cx="92" cy="101" r="7" fill="url(#striaFlow)" fill-opacity="0.8" />
                     <circle class="stria-tx stria-tx--c" cx="92" cy="133" r="7" fill="url(#striaFlow)" fill-opacity="0.6" />
                   </svg>
                 </div>
               </div>
             </div>
           </div>

           <!-- Phase 4: Calib (Right Side) -->
           <div class="relative mb-16">
             <div class="lg:flex items-center">
               <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-12">
                 <div class="consensus-anim consensus-anim--calib" aria-hidden="true">
                   <div class="consensus-anim__label">Calib: verify + watchdog</div>
                   <svg class="consensus-anim__svg" viewBox="0 0 320 180" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" focusable="false">
                     <defs>
                       <linearGradient id="calibGlow" x1="0" y1="0" x2="320" y2="0" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                         <stop stop-color="#FBBF24" stop-opacity="0.95" />
                         <stop offset="1" stop-color="#F59E0B" stop-opacity="0.95" />
                       </linearGradient>
                     </defs>

                     <rect x="42" y="48" width="236" height="84" rx="18" stroke="#FBBF24" stroke-opacity="0.3" stroke-width="2" />

                     <rect x="66" y="74" width="70" height="32" rx="12" fill="#FBBF24" fill-opacity="0.15" stroke="#FBBF24" stroke-opacity="0.4" />
                     <rect x="184" y="74" width="70" height="32" rx="12" fill="#FBBF24" fill-opacity="0.15" stroke="#FBBF24" stroke-opacity="0.4" />

                     <path d="M146 90h28" stroke="url(#calibGlow)" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-opacity="0.55" />
                     <path class="calib-check" d="M156 90l6 6 12-14" stroke="url(#calibGlow)" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />

                     <circle class="calib-pulse" cx="270" cy="90" r="10" fill="url(#calibGlow)" fill-opacity="0.7" />
                     <circle class="calib-pulse-ring" cx="270" cy="90" r="10" stroke="url(#calibGlow)" stroke-width="3" stroke-opacity="0.65" />
                   </svg>
                 </div>
               </div>
               <div class="hidden lg:block absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-amber-600 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-900 shadow-lg shadow-amber-500/50"></div>
               <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-12">
                 <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500/20 to-amber-600/10 border border-amber-500/30 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-amber-500/30 transition-all duration-300">
                   <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                     <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-amber-600 rounded-lg p-3 mr-4">
                       <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                         <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path>
                       </svg>
                     </div>
                     <div>
                       <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-amber-400 mb-1">LAYER 4 • VERIFY</div>
                       <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Calib</h3>
                     </div>
                   </div>
                   <p class="text-slate-200 mb-4">Calibration + watchdog layer (aka Arb) that verifies execution results across Striae and coordinates recovery actions during stalls.</p>
                   <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
                     <li class="flex items-start">
                       <span class="text-amber-400 mr-2">•</span>
                       Verifies execution outcomes and state roots
                     </li>
